            "subtype": "action_type",
            "type": "stat_block_section"
          },
          "effect": "The morlock throws himself in front of his master, taking half the damage of the attack (before applying any weaknesses or resistances). Vikandian takes the remaining damage, applying any weaknesses or resistances as normal.",
          "name": "Mortal Shield",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "trigger": "The morlock thrall will do anything to protect their master. If the morlock thrall is adjacent to Vikandian when Vikandian would take damage from a Strike or spell attack",
          "type": "stat_block_section"
        }
