            "name": "Revel in the Gore",
            "requirement": "The morlock thrall's previous action was a critical hit with a melee Strike; Effect The morlock shrieks in excitement and springs forward to slurp at the gore. Any creatures within 20 feet who can see the disgusting display must attempt a DC 21 Fortitude save or become sickened 1 (or sickened 2 on a critical failure). Vampires and other morlocks in the area are emboldened instead and gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Will saves until the end of their next turn.",
